name: Winter Kate-Velvet trouser
description: A great investment, velvet pants from Winter Kate.  A wonderful addition to the Autumn/Winter wardrobe.  Add the highest of heels and team with Winter Kate's fabulous cream embelished cuff shirt and go.  Concealed zip ankle detail.  Pockets and fastening at the waist with hidden zip. 79% viscose 21% silk. Hand Wash.
